narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes, if you're interested in Korean!
An excellent class, after which you'll see your Korean skills increase markedly from 1st semester - Lee SSN is a clear, energetic teacher who values a friendly class environment
I would recommend KREN 120 to another student. It's a fun course that allows you to improve your Korean a lot!

Like all language classes, Korean requires a lot of patience and practice. You get to bond with your classmates and even befriend your language professor. It tends to be a bit more laid back than other classes but it makes it more fun to learn the language.
